    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tamamoji is a clicker game on which you have to take care of your emoji.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Actions</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hydrate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sleep</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scold</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comfort</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy an upgrade for your tamamoji to improve its quality of life!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatic points per second</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additive points per click</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Points multiplier depending on the tamamoji mood</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bonus game mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also contains a little clicker on which you start with the mood of a tamamoji and you have to reach all the moods available to finish the game!</p>",
